latestPosts.caption:
RCB has my heart ❤️! 
I officially declare myself as a Kohlipaglu 🎀
I've travelled miles, cheered till my voice was hoarse, and felt every emotion for this team. 
I've been on cloud nine with every victory and felt the weight of defeat. But through it all, my love for this team has only grown stronger. 
What a perfect ending to an incredible journey!! Slept like a baby last night, with a heart full of joy and a smile on my face. 
Thanks, RCB, for the memories that I'll cherish forever.
